# Cardoil Avantaj ŌĆö Design System

You are responsible for maintaining visual consistency across this Next.js marketing site for **Cardoil Avantaj** (Romanian B2B transport & fuel broker).

The site uses the **Translo Home-2** theme as its primary UI layer, with **Tailwind v4 + shadcn/ui** for forms and a few legacy inner-page blocks. Follow the rules below ŌĆö do not mix patterns arbitrarily.

---

## Source of truth (read before styling)

| File | Role |
|------|------|
| `src/styles/translo/index.css` | Translo theme entry ŌĆö Bootstrap, module CSS, icomoon, brand overrides |
| `src/styles/translo/color-1.css` | Brand primary override (`--thm-primary: #00a44f`) scoped to `.homeTwo` |
| `src/styles/translo/react-adjustment.css` | React/Swiper fixes ŌĆö add overrides here, not in vendor CSS |
| `src/app/globals.css` | Tailwind tokens, shadcn theme, brand utilities for forms |
| `src/app/layout.tsx` | Site shell: `body-dark-bg homeTwo` + `TransloHeader` / `TransloFooter` |
| `src/lib/content.ts` | Copy, nav, images, services, stats ŌĆö not styling |
| `src/lib/pexels.ts` | Pexels fallback URLs when CDN/local images fail |
| `components.json` | shadcn/ui config (`base-nova`, Base UI) |

**Import order in layout:** `globals.css` then `@/styles/translo/index.css`.

When changing brand green, update **`color-1.css`** (`--thm-primary`) and **`globals.css`** (`--brand`, `--ring`) together.

