## Brand colors

### Translo theme (pages, heroes, CTAs, icons)

| Token | Value | Use for |
|-------|-------|---------|
| `--thm-primary` | `#00a44f` | CTAs (`.thm-btn`), accents, links, counter highlights |
| `--thm-black` | `#121213` | Headings, dark text |
| `--thm-white` | `#ffffff` | Text on dark backgrounds |
| `--thm-gray-bg` | `#f8f8f8` | Light section backgrounds |

Scoped under `:root .homeTwo` in `color-1.css`. Use Translo classes ŌĆö do not hardcode `#00a44f` in components.

### Tailwind / shadcn (forms, legacy blocks)

| Token | Tailwind | Use for |
|-------|----------|---------|
| `--brand` | `bg-brand`, `text-brand` | Form buttons, focus rings |
| `--brand-accent` | `#faf031` | Highlights in Tailwind sections |
| `--navy` | `bg-navy`, `text-navy` | Legacy navy sections on `/despre` |
| `--primary`, `--muted`, `--card`, `--border` | shadcn UI chrome | Inputs, cards, accordions |

**Rules:**
- Translo sections: rely on `--thm-*` via theme CSS
- Form fields: shadcn `Input` / `Textarea` with `ContactForm variant="dark"` on dark panels
- Never use raw hex in JSX ŌĆö use CSS variables

