## Typography

Translo loads **Rubik** (headings) and **Krub** (body) via `index.css`.

| Pattern | Use for |
|---------|---------|
| `.sec-title-two` + `.sub-title h5` | Section eyebrows |
| `.sec-title-two h2` | Section headings |
| `.thm-btn` + `.txt` | Primary CTAs |
| icomoon `<span className="icon-*" />` or `<i className="icon-*">` | Decorative / UI icons |

**Rules:**
- Prefer Translo title blocks over ad-hoc heading classes on themed pages
- Site language is Romanian (`lang="ro"`) ŌĆö preserve diacritics
- Lucide icons only inside shadcn components, not Translo sections

