## Layout & spacing

| Pattern | Use for |
|---------|---------|
| `.padding` | Default vertical section rhythm (Translo) |
| `.container` + `.row` + `.col-*` | Bootstrap grid ŌĆö match existing pages |
| `TransloPageHeader` | Inner page hero (breadcrumb + title) |
| `.section` / `.container-page` | **Legacy Tailwind only** ŌĆö `/despre` mixed blocks |

**Rules:**
- Inner pages: `TransloPageHeader` then `<section className="ŌĆ” padding">` with `.container`
- Do not nest `.container` inside `.container`
- Reuse existing Translo section class names (`about-two`, `services-two`, `contact-one`) when extending pages

