## Images

- **Primary CDN:** `cardoilavantaj.ro` via `content.ts`
- **Local theme assets:** `/img/ŌĆ”` (shapes, backgrounds from Translo)
- **Fallbacks:** `FallbackImage`, `FallbackBackground`, `SiteImage` with `fallbackKey` from `pexels.ts`
- Remote patterns in `next.config.ts`: `cardoilavantaj.ro`, `images.pexels.com`
- Meaningful `alt` text in Romanian; `sizes` on Next.js `Image`

Decorative icomoon icons: `aria-hidden="true"`.

